OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1773914712
OL,3,CMan who strangled stepmum with
OL,4,Cheadscarf guilty of murder
OL,6,FA man who strangled his step-mother
OL,7,Fwith her own headscarf after searching
OL,8,Finheritance websites has been
OL,9,Fconvicted of murder.
OL,11,FRizwana Kousar, 41, was found
OL,12,Funconscious in the bath at her home on
OL,13,FKensington Road in Bradford on 15
OL,14,FAugust 2023. She died two days later.
OL,16,FHer stepson Abdul Sami claimed he had
OL,17,Ffound her in the bath before calling
OL,18,F999.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1773914712
OL,3,CMan who strangled stepmum with
OL,4,Cheadscarf guilty of murder
OL,6,FWhen investigations revealed Mrs
OL,7,FKousar had a red mark on her neck,
OL,8,FSami claimed it happened when he
OL,9,Fremoved the scarf to perform CPR.
OL,11,FHis mobile phone showed he had visited
OL,12,Fwebsites about inheritance three
OL,13,Fmonths before the murder and had
OL,14,Flooked at a website with the question:
OL,15,F"Does a killer inherit from their
OL,16,Fvictim's estate?"
OL,18,FOn the day of the attack he looked at
OL,19,Fanother site asking: "What is the
OL,20,Fchance of survival if the brain is
OL,21,Fstarved of oxygen?"
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1773914712
OL,3,CMan who strangled stepmum with
OL,4,Cheadscarf guilty of murder
OL,6,FSami was found guilty of murder on
OL,7,FTuesday. He will be sentenced on 20
OL,8,FMarch.
OL,10,FIn a tribute Mrs Kousar's family said
OL,11,Fshe was a "cherished daughter, sister,
OL,12,Fauntie, and friend".
OL,14,FThey added: "The void she has left is
OL,15,Fimmeasurable, and our hearts are
OL,16,Fshattered by her absence.
OL,18,F"Nothing can erase the profound pain
OL,19,Fand devastation that has engulfed our
OL,20,Ffamily."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
