FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1773914712
OL,3,CMan who strangled stepmum with
OL,4,Cheadscarf guilty of murder
OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Matt Holdsworth, of the
OL,7,FWest Yorkshire Police Homicide and
OL,8,FMajor Enquiry Team, said: "This was a
OL,9,Fdeeply tragic case, and our thoughts
OL,10,Fremain with the family, and everyone
OL,11,Faffected by Rizwana's death.
OL,13,F"This investigation has involved
OL,14,Fcomplex and technical investigation
OL,15,Fwhich has taken significant time to
OL,16,Freach this point."
